                      | . Then 
                      strong: a(href=`mailto:${data.contactEmail}`) drop us
                      |  an email and ask for discount.
                section(class="feature 4u 12u$(small)")
                  h3.title 
                    i.fa.fa-percent
                    |  Discount for sponsors
                  div
                    p 
                      | We provide sponsors with discount for supporting the event. Please 
                      strong: a(href=`mailto:${data.contactEmail}`) contact us
                      |  and receive an exclusive sponsorship offer.



